data.description: POOL HOME WITH LANAI AND BASKETBALL COURT!! This is such a wonderful house to enjoy outside activities and entertain.  Enter into large foyer and to the left is an office or bonus room. Large Great room with wood burning fireplace with gorgeous mantle. Open kitchen is ideal for the flow of company and guest.  3 large bedrooms and 2 baths.  Master bathroom features a huge walk in closet, double vanity, separate shower and soaking tub.  20x12 Shed/shop, privacy fenced back yard.
